***** Textalk *****

Communication tool for hard-of hearing people.

You can make text message with voice recognition, text input or handwriting,
And show it to hard-of hearing people.

You can also send it each other via WiFi network when both of you have phone or tablet.

This application is useful for those who want to communicate silently.
For example, in the classroom.

